not all of them are production-ready.

00:05:50.440 --> 00:05:54.440
So I think it's actually a good thing that 85% of models don't make it into production

00:05:54.440 --> 00:06:00.440
for both quality and cost-saving reasons.

00:06:00.440 --> 00:06:02.440
So I gave my dog information.

00:06:03.440 --> 00:06:07.440
And at home, there was a great response and a reproducible response.

00:06:07.440 --> 00:06:12.440
But out in the wilderness of my suburban neighborhood, when I gave my dog instructions, it didn't

00:06:12.440 --> 00:06:15.440
look the same.

00:06:15.440 --> 00:06:18.440
Things behave differently in different environments.

00:06:18.440 --> 00:06:21.440
Models work the same way as Little Toasty.

