It's from scikit-learn.

00:15:31.440 --> 00:15:33.440
We can see the size of the model.

00:15:33.440 --> 00:15:35.440
We can see a hash.

00:15:35.440 --> 00:15:37.440
The very specific version.

00:15:37.440 --> 00:15:42.440
And we can see that user ptype right there for what the data should look like.

00:15:42.440 --> 00:15:48.440
We can also see what the required packages are to run this model.

00:15:48.440 --> 00:15:53.440
So we were talking about, you know, collaborating with your teammates.

