So where else can you put these boards?

00:16:06.440 --> 00:16:08.440
We started with our temporary board.

00:16:08.440 --> 00:16:10.440
But you could also have a local board.

00:16:10.440 --> 00:16:12.440
Maybe you just wanted it kind of on a local machine.

00:16:12.440 --> 00:16:17.440
Or if you wanted to put this on prem, maybe a local board is the right move.

00:16:17.440 --> 00:16:19.440
But it gets more interesting.

00:16:19.440 --> 00:16:22.440
So you can also just switch out board to S3.

00:16:22.440 --> 00:16:25.440
And you can host this on Amazon Web Services.

00:16:25.440 --> 00:16:28.440
You can host it on Google Cloud Storage.

00:16:28.440 --> 00:16:33.440
You can pin models to Microsoft Azure Blob Storage as well.

00:16:33.440 --> 00:16:37.440
You might have to add a few more arguments to, like, give the right credentials.

00:16:37.440 --> 00:16:41.440
