00:44:50.439 --> 00:44:53.439
Why did you choose the name Vetiver?

00:44:53.439 --> 00:44:56.439
So if you're into perfumery,

00:44:56.439 --> 00:45:01.439
Vetiver is actually a stabilizing agent in perfumes.

00:45:01.439 --> 00:45:04.439
So we kind of thought, like my team and I,

00:45:04.439 --> 00:45:07.439
that, you know, ML Ops is this crazy space,

00:45:07.439 --> 00:45:11.439
but we want something that is a stabilizing agent for your models,

00:45:11.439 --> 00:45:13.439
and so we chose the name Vetiver.

00:45:13.439 --> 00:45:14.439
It's a real plant.

00:45:14.439 --> 00:45:18.439
I think you can grow it and eat it or whatever,

00:45:18.439 --> 00:45:20.439
but that is how the name came to be.

00:45:20.439 --> 00:45:21.439
That's deep.

