00:46:06.439 --> 00:46:08.439
So they don't really change.

00:46:08.439 --> 00:46:11.439
If you're developing somewhere else,

00:46:11.439 --> 00:46:14.439
you kind of can use these same practices.

00:46:14.439 --> 00:46:17.439
You're still able to do these tasks.

00:46:17.439 --> 00:46:20.439
They're still important tasks to do,

00:46:20.439 --> 00:46:23.439
regardless of the size of your model.

