00:48:04.439 --> 00:48:09.439
Is this if you don't version, maybe?

00:48:09.439 --> 00:48:11.439
I guess you could overversion.

00:48:11.439 --> 00:48:13.439
Maybe you don't need to save all your models,

00:48:13.439 --> 00:48:15.439
and then you spend a lot of money on cloud storage

00:48:15.439 --> 00:48:17.439
that you don't need to.

